creator: StarInix
descriptionHtml:
Are you frequently scrambling on medical coding book pages or hard to use software and websites for diagnostics and procedure codes? Are you tired of having outdated information when you are coding? iCoder gives you a way to find the right codes every time with it's always up to date, modern and easy to use search interface right on your device.

Are you a medical provider or medical coder? You can quickly find CPT-4 ® with their RVUs, ICD-10-CM, ICD10-PCS, HCPCS codes using iCoder's intuitive interface including Major Diagnostic Categories (MDCs) and Diagnostic Related Group (DRGs) right from code the details.

Do you do anesthesia coding ? iCoder can quickly identify anesthesia codes and calculate fees.

Are you part of a laboratory or do you work with durable medical equipment? Quickly find Clinical Lab Fee Schedule (CLFS) and Durable Medical Equipment (DME) rates for all CPT® codes.

iCoder has been on the market for more than 10 years and you can now try it risk-free for 30 days, no commitment on your part is required, we'll never charge you if you do not subscribe!

We guarantee that you will be able to find the right codes every-time. We also promise to always keep the codes up to date with the latest releases and tell you when they change. We'll also return your call or email within 24 hours and solve any issues you might have within just a few days. If we don't live up to any of these promises, we insist that you tell us and we'll refund your purchase and give you iCoder for free for a year at our cost so we can fix or improve what you found.

*** What our customers say about iCoder: ***

"If you are like me you want to know RIGHT THEN if what you're billing is accurate, needs a modifier, & most importantly what the UCR is to assure you meet your cost of service! You get all of this @ your fingertips w/o taking 45 min thumbing through an ICD 10 or CPT book that's 10 inches thick! Get rid of your books & have it all in ONE app!" by bfrensley

"Quick, accurate, intuitive and easy to use. I especially like the ability to create my "favorites" list for faster reference. Worth every penny!"

GPCI, RVU and Anesthesia Base Units
Select your GPCI location to see RVU values specific to your location.

Smart Code Search
Get results for queries with typos such as 'asthmo' and partial words such as 'ten fing'. Quickly switch from CPT/HCPCS, ICD10-CM and ICD10-PCS.

Always Up to Date
Quickly see when the last update to the codes was done and get notified when new updates are available

Specialty Guide
Browse CPT ® codes by specialty

Anesthesia
Use the anesthesia fee calculator to quickly and easily see anesthesia fees for your services. See ASA Crosswalk® for your selected codes on iCoder Standard.

Modifiers
Browse CPT Level I Modifiers, Category II Moidifiers, HCPCS modifiers and more

ICD10-CM / ICD10-PCS
Browse by the ICD10 chapters or build PCS codes step by step by constructing the code structure. Includes MDC and DRG codes for all codes and code edits such as Female Only, Male Only, Maternity, Newborn, Pediatric, Adult Only and Manifestation Code.

CPT® Legend information
See indicators for new codes, revised codes, add-on codes, FDA approval pending, modifier 51 and more

Favorites
Keep unlimited list of your favorite codes with as many folders as you want, using iCoder 2018,2019? Bring all your favorites to iCoder 2021 with the touch of a button and instantly see the differences between the payment rates.

Synchronization
Your favorites and recent codes are securely stored on the cloud and synchronized to all your devices automatically, allowing you to use iCoder off-line.

Working Off-line
Use on your iPad, iPhone and Mac even when off-line, synchronizes when connected.

Please contact support@icoder.app for any questions.
